These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, action, thriller, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, folk, hip-hop, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, british, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, motorbike, helicopter
1. the egyptian is the fan of ambient##1
2. the british is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching drama movies##2
3. the egyptian is the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the mexican is on the far right##1
9. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | drama   | horror  | thriller  |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | ambient    | funk      | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | egyptian | british | mexican |
| Transport     | helicopter  | skateboard       | train    | motorbike     |

