.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, rock-climbing, magic-tricks, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, sports, disaster, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, turtle, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, snowboarding, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person watching fantasy movies and the owner of the goldfish##2
7. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing | rock-climbing    | magic-tricks  | camping    |
| Movie-Genre   | family      | sports  | fantasy  | disaster |
| Pet           | goldfish      | turtle       | rabbit      | horse       |
| Sport         | cycling    | weightlifting | snowboarding | biathlon |

