.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, cucumber, nectarine, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, chess, cooking, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, videographer, fisherman, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, boat, trike, bus
1. the fisherman is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the videographer is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person eating kale is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is baking##2
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person eating nectarine and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | cucumber | nectarine     | kale   | pumpkin     |
| Hobby       | chess   | gardening   | cooking | baking |
| Job         | police-officer   | fisherman | mechanic       | videographer    |
| Transport   | trike    | boat | car  | bus    |

