.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, writer, project-manager, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, family, superhero, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, turtle, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, tennis, climbing
 1. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the software-developer##1
 3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the cat##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person watching family movies is the project-manager##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the writer is between the owner of the dog and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | software-developer  | accountant | writer     | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | sports  | superhero | family       |
| Pet           | cat       | hedgehog    | turtle      | dog           |
| Sport         | basketball | golf   | climbing   | tennis         |

