.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, onion, broccoli, lettuce
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, teacher, coach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, superhero, martial-arts, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball, rugby, biathlon
