 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
 3. the teacher is the person eating onion##1
 4. the teacher is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the coach is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 8. the doctor is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person watching satire movies##2
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | onion         | broccoli         | kiwi     | lettuce      |
| Job           | teacher | coach | dancer    | doctor     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | martial-arts       | western    | superhero       |
