2. the bartender is between the fan of gospel and the nigerian##2
3. the thai is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the indian##2
4. the fisherman is on the left of the indian##1
5. the thai is the thai##1
6. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the indian is on the left of the dancer##1
8. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
9. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
