 5. the canadian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 7. the malaysian is the person driving the trike##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the pakistani is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
