4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the bus and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
6. the person drinking 7up is the person watching spy movies##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

