The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, project-manager, security-guard, chef
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, trance, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, surfing, badminton
 1. the person eating cherry is the security-guard##1
 2. the person eating carrot is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the security-guard is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person eating cucumber##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left of the security-guard##1
 8. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
 9. the coach is between the chef and the person who's sport is rowing##2
10. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot        | kiwi    | cucumber | cherry   |
