There 4 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, pomegranate, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, puzzles, writing, camping
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, goat, mouse
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 4. the person eating avocado is the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating avocado and the person eating pomegranate##2
 9. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person eating avocado and the person eating pomegranate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | juice    | soy-milk    | cola      | iced-tea |
| Food       | avocado        | pumpkin       | pomegranate       | cabbage     |
| Hobby      | writing | video-games | camping | puzzles        |
| Pet        | rabbit       | mouse     | goat         | chinchilla           |

