The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, airplane, tram, trike
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the bird##2
 6. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating tomato##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the person driving the tram##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | kiwi  | tomato | eggplant     | pear     |
| Pet         | bird | chinchilla | mouse     | snake |
| Sport       | skiing  | swimming   | volleyball | cycling    |
| Transport   | tram   | airplane   | boat  | trike        |

